r>Me and Xerxus(60th cleric) once  killed a lvl 60 mob , all due to tashing it and landing roots.Damn thought destroyer took 20 min. but we dropped it.grats again finn on the ring.<br><br>And palies get to know the location of XI thall. the 35 ac flowing cape is soo amazing.<br>Here is how ya pull him.get a levitae and sow, stached behind a bunch a crap buffs.Move to the hill behind the area, and use a telescope to target him.<br>next move beside the house on the water. levitated.<br>here is the tricky part... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>If you are 60, use sanc, and nuke him, and zone.<br>If ya aint 60, nuke him, DA and zone. I have done both, and well the first way works soo much better.<br><br>well if ya need tidbits a info ask me , and Ill post my knowledge.<br><br>Chakail Malach<br>60th palie of VZ<br>Officer of Iron Tower<br>and many other things that I dont need to mention<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urendaelbrigh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rendael Brigh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 52<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/30/02 6:55:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm15.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Soloing in the Grey</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> If you are 60, use <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> sanc</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>What does that mean. <p>Rendael Brigh<BR>Knight of Truth, 56th shield<BR>Avengers Federation<BR>Tholuxe Paells<BR>Master Smith 208<BR>Master Brewer 146<BR>Master Potter 124<BR>Journeyman Tailor